For some reason all these hide-IP programs (how many are there, 6 or 7?) install the Ask toolbar on your browser without even giving you a choice. I got rid of the toolbar using Your! Uninstaller in the super mode -- it even cleans out the registry entries.
Works perfectly fine on windows 7 Ult 64bit.
